To abtain all focussed image

1. Install openCV
2. run the following commands in the extracted directory
	jai@server:~/jai/OpenCV/segment$ make
	jai@server:~/jai/OpenCV/segment$ ./segment 0.7 700 100 data5-*.jpg 20

--> press any key when done.

total number of arguments: 8

./segment sigma k min input1 input2 input3 input4 max_shift_for_anaglyph
